  <data name="_1ConnectionRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Islands with a maximum of one bridge can set their connection if there is only one neighbor island accepting bridges. Neighbor islands with a maximum of one bridge cannot be connected to as both islands would be isolated then.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_2ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of two bridges has two neighbor islands with also a maximum of two bridges, then a connection to each neighbors must be set.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_2ConnectionsRule2" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of two bridges has a connection to another island with max one connections, then the other connection can only go to a neighbor with max connections &gt; 1.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_3ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of three bridges has only two neighbors, then a connection must be set to each neighbor.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_4ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Islands with a maximum of four bridges can set all connections if only two neighbors are available.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_4ConnectionsRule2" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Islands with a maximum of four bridges and three neighbors can set one connection to each neighbor if one of the neighbors already has a connection to the island and has max connections.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_5ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of five connections has three neighbors then each needs one connection.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_6ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of six connections has three neighbors then set all connections.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_7ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of seven connections has four neighbors then each needs one connection.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="_8ConnectionsRule1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>If an island with a maximum of eight connections has four neighbors then set all connections.</value>
